<title>UK: UBS sets call warrants on Alusuisse.</title>
<headline>UBS sets call warrants on Alusuisse.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Union Bank of Switzerland said it has issued 25 million American-style call warrants on registered shares of Alusuisse-Lonza Holding AG.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 50 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    1,350 CHF		 PREMIUM	15.9 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     2.15 CHF		  GEARING	11.6 TIMES</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 09.MAY.97-16.OCT.98   PAYDATE	09.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWX			 MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  1,257 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
